# PLATFORMS
* Ubuntu latest stable and stable currently the *only* supported host platform *

### Linux
  _dpkg_ : 
	.- *apt* `build-essential`
  _rpm_ :
	.- *yum* `groupinstall "Development Tools"`
  _arch_ :
	.- *pacman* `base-devel scons python-mongo`

## General prerequisites
  _MongoDB 3.x built in python venv_
	.- *default* `python 3.8+ w/ pipenv --python=3.6`
  _WSGI middleware_
	.- *default* `uwsgi`
  _HTTP/1 middleware_
	.- *default* `nginx # reverse proxy`
  _CFG w/ ffi_
	.- *default* `r2pipe`
  _Container runtime_
	.- *default* `containerd # docker`
# End of PLATFORMS.md
